OL,3,CMental health patients twice as likely
OL,4,Cto wait 12 hours in A&E
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Health Correspondent
OL,7,FRebecca Barry and Health and Science
OL,8,FProducer Philip Sime
OL,10,FPatients suffering a crisis in England
OL,11,Fare twice as likely to wait more than
OL,12,F12 hours in A&E, ITV News can reveal.
OL,14,FFigures obtained by the Royal College
OL,15,Fof Emergency Medicine and shared
OL,16,Fexclusively with ITV News show mental
OL,17,Fhealth patients are disproportionately
OL,18,Fimpacted by A&E delays, with one-in-
OL,19,Ffour mental health patients had long
OL,20,Fwaits in 2023, compared to one-in-ten
OL,21,Fof all other patients.
