OL,3,CMental health patients twice as likely
OL,4,Cto wait 12 hours in A&E
OL,6,FWhile prolonged waits for all patients
OL,7,Fdecreased slightly, the proportion of
OL,8,Fmental health patients waiting 12
OL,9,Fhours to be admitted surged to an all
OL,10,Ftime high of 23%.
OL,12,FIn 2019, just 7% of mental health
OL,13,Fpatients waited that long.
OL,15,FEmma Powell has schizoaffective
OL,16,Fdisorder. Last year, while suffering a
OL,17,Fmental health crisis, she attended A&E
OL,18,Fand waited 87 hours, or three-and-a-
OL,19,Fhalf days, for treatment.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/11
