OL,3,CMental health patients twice as likely
OL,4,Cto wait 12 hours in A&E
OL,6,F"It's distressing," Ms Powell told ITV
OL,7,FNews. "It's not a place that's
OL,8,Fdesigned for you to be in for a long
OL,9,Fperiod of time."
OL,11,F"I found it really difficult being in
OL,12,Fthere. It took 11 hours before I was
OL,13,Fgiven a trolley to lie on and would be
OL,14,Fjust lying on the floor in the waiting
OL,15,Froom. It's not a situation or
OL,16,Fenvironment that's conducive to
OL,17,Fhealing or getting better," she added.
OL,19,FThe frustration extends beyond
OL,20,Fpatients and onto the staff in the
OL,21,Femergency departments as well.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/11
