OL,3,CMental health patients twice as likely
OL,4,Cto wait 12 hours in A&E
OL,6,F"You just do feel so, so helpless,"
OL,7,Fsaid Kath O'Hagan, Matron at the Royal
OL,8,FBerkshire Hospital's Emergency
OL,9,FDepartment.
OL,11,F"It's the fact that we know we're not
OL,12,Fdoing the best for our patients and
OL,13,Fthat's really, really hard.
OL,15,F"We just try to be kind and supportive
OL,16,Fand all of those things you try to do
OL,17,Fwhen someone is in distress but what
OL,18,Fwe can't do is offer the actual mental
OL,19,Fhealth care."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/11
