OL,6,FBut some Trusts have set up spaces
OL,7,Fwhich are dedicated to emergency
OL,8,Fmental health treatment.
OL,10,FAt Lincoln County Hospital, a new
OL,11,FMental Health Urgent Assessment Centre
OL,12,Freceives around 50 patients every
OL,13,Fweek, all of whom would have
OL,14,Fpreviously attended A&E.
OL,16,FAmy, who lives with a personality
OL,17,Fdisorder, PTSD and psychosis, says the
OL,18,Fservice has been life changing.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/11
