OL,4,Cto wait 12 hours in A&E
OL,6,F"They've all made me get to a point in
OL,7,Fmy life where I can go out and start
OL,8,Fearning money and just become more
OL,9,Fself-sufficient," she told ITV News.
OL,11,FLeading figures in emergency medicine
OL,12,Fsay the situation is "shameful".
OL,14,F"People who come to A&E when
OL,15,Fexperiencing mental health crises or
OL,16,Fextreme mental ill heath are among the
OL,17,Fmost vulnerable patients we see," Dr
OL,18,FAdrian Boyle, President of the Royal
OL,19,FCollege of Emergency Medicine, said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/11
