OL,4,Cto wait 12 hours in A&E
OL,6,F"This data shows so starkly how badly
OL,7,Fthey are being let down by a
OL,8,Ffragmented system and the shameful
OL,9,Fwaits they are enduring. It is simply
OL,10,Funacceptable."
OL,12,FVictoria Atkins, the Secretary of
OL,13,FState for Health and Social Care,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Of course we apologise to
OL,15,Feveryone who waits for longer than we
OL,16,Fwould want in A&E."
