OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care said: "We have
OL,8,Fincreased overall mental health
OL,9,Ffunding by #4.7 billion since 2018 and
OL,10,Fare investing #150 million in mental
OL,11,Fhealth urgent and emergency care
OL,12,Finfrastructure, including alternative
OL,13,Foptions to A&E and inpatient care to
OL,14,Fhelp improve patients' experience and
OL,15,Fease the pressure on emergency
OL,16,Fdepartments and ambulance services.
