OL,6,F"We are working with NHS England to
OL,7,Freduce the waits of mental health
OL,8,Fpatients in A&E, including the
OL,9,Favailability of Approved Mental Health
OL,10,FProfessionals to speed up assessments.
OL,12,F"In addition, we are supporting the
OL,13,FNHS to deliver the highest standard of
OL,14,Fcare possible and ensure people get
OL,15,Fthe emergency care they need. Our
OL,16,FUrgent and Emergency Care Recovery
OL,17,FPlan has already added an extra 5,000
OL,18,Fhospital beds, while A&E four-hour
OL,19,Fperformance improved in February
OL,20,Fcompared to January."
