OL,6,FA spokesperson for NHS England said:
OL,7,F"While we recognise there is more to
OL,8,Fdo, all emergency department services
OL,9,Fnow offer 24/7 access to a mental
OL,10,Fhealth liaison service or local crisis
OL,11,Fsupport with 92% of these provided by
OL,12,Fan on-site liaison service, up from
OL,13,F66% in 2018.
OL,15,F"The NHS has also set up 24/7 mental
OL,16,Fhealth crisis lines across England
OL,17,Fwhich receive up to 200,000 calls a
OL,18,Fmonth, with only a fraction of people
OL,19,Fthen going needing further support in
OL,20,FA&E."
